<item>
<title><code>mode</code></title>
  <p>A <link xref="Cogl.VerticesMode"/> defining how to draw the vertices</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>n_vertices</code></title>
  <p>The number of vertices to process when drawing</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>attributes</code></title>
